        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>利用shell限制一段时间内zabbix的告警消息数<br>通过shell发送消息到企业微信应用<br>缓存企业微信token避免重复获取</p></blockquote><h3 id="告警抑制"><a href="#告警抑制" class="headerlink" title="告警抑制"></a>告警抑制</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br><span class="line">132</span><br><span class="line">133</span><br><span class="line">134</span><br><span class="line">135</span><br><span class="line">136</span><br><span class="line">137</span><br><span class="line">138</span><br><span class="line">139</span><br><span class="line">140</span><br><span class="line">141</span><br><span class="line">142</span><br><span class="line">143</span><br><span class="line">144</span><br><span class="line">145</span><br><span class="line">146</span><br><span class="line">147</span><br><span class="line">148</span><br><span class="line">149</span><br><span class="line">150</span><br><span class="line">151</span><br><span class="line">152</span><br><span class="line">153</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># zabbix控制台</span></span><br><span class="line">zabbix_url=<span class="string">&#x27;http://zabbix_url/zabbix.php?action=dashboard.view&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置日志文件的路径,尽量丢内存目录里</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> [  -d /dev/shm ];<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">    WATCH_DIRS=<span class="string">&quot;/dev/shm&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    WATCH_DIRS=<span class="string">&quot;/tmp/zabbix&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ALTER_LOG=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;WATCH_DIRS&#125;</span>/zabbix_alter.log&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">LOCK_LAST=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;WATCH_DIRS&#125;</span>/last_notify.lock&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将告警信息放到一个文件中</span></span><br><span class="line">TOTAL_ALTER_LOG=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;WATCH_DIRS&#125;</span>/total_alter.txt&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;`date +&#x27;%F %T&#x27;` ---------------------------------&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; <span class="variable">$&#123;TOTAL_ALTER_LOG&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;$*&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; <span class="variable">$&#123;TOTAL_ALTER_LOG&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 告警次数，当十分钟内告警的次数大于这个数，则进行告警抑制</span></span><br><span class="line">WARN_COUNTER=4</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取十分钟之前的时间戳，方便后面进行对比</span></span><br><span class="line">AGOTIME=`<span class="built_in">date</span> -d <span class="string">&#x27;10 min ago&#x27;</span> +<span class="string">&#x27;%s&#x27;</span>`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取告警的信息</span></span><br><span class="line">SEND_TOMAIL=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">SEND_SUB=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$2</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">SEND_CONTENTS=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$3</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">[ -z <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;SEND_SUB&#125;</span>&quot;</span> ] &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;not content to send, exit.&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 检查实际的发送告警的脚本是否存在</span></span><br><span class="line">CURRENT_PATH=$(<span class="built_in">cd</span> `<span class="built_in">dirname</span> <span class="variable">$0</span>` &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">pwd</span>)</span><br><span class="line">SCRIPT_FILE=<span class="variable">$&#123;CURRENT_PATH&#125;</span>/send_to_wechat_app.sh</span><br><span class="line">[ ! -f <span class="variable">$&#123;SCRIPT_FILE&#125;</span> ] &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;SCRIPT_FILE&#125;</span> NOT FOUND, exit.&quot;</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取接收人</span></span><br><span class="line">CONTACT_NAME=<span class="variable">$&#123;SEND_TOMAIL%%@*&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取现在的时间戳</span></span><br><span class="line">NOWTIME=`<span class="built_in">date</span> +<span class="string">&#x27;%s&#x27;</span>`</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置CHANGE变量，当变量为1的时候，发送抑制的告警信息</span></span><br><span class="line">CHANGE=0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置一个关键字，做为后面判断是异常告警还是恢复告警</span></span><br><span class="line">MARK=<span class="string">&#x27;default&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 告警信息中必须包含ok/error字段</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取告警信息中的字段，包含[error]则为异常告警，[ok]则是恢复告警</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> `<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;2&#125;</span><span class="variable">$&#123;3&#125;</span>&quot;</span>|egrep -i <span class="string">&quot;\[error\]&quot;</span> &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1`;<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">    MARK=<span class="string">&#x27;ERROR&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">elif</span> `<span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;2&#125;</span><span class="variable">$&#123;3&#125;</span>&quot;</span>|egrep -i <span class="string">&quot;\[ok\]&quot;</span> &gt;/dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1`;<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">    MARK=<span class="string">&#x27;OK&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 统计$&#123;WATCH_DIRS&#125;目录下alter.log文件中$&#123;MARK&#125;标记的个数, 当大于$&#123;WARN_COUNTER&#125;值时,有两种方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. 判断$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;锁文件,如果此文件存在,则直接退出</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. 如果$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;锁文件不存在的时候, 发送LAST最后一条消息</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function"><span class="title">ALL_TO_ALL</span></span>() &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> [[ <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;MARK&#125;</span>&quot;</span> != <span class="string">&quot;default&quot;</span>  ]];<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 将收件人、时间戳、告警状态的字段放入一个临时文件中</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 一条代表发生了一次告警</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># xxx@123487@OK</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;CONTACT_NAME&#125;</span>@<span class="variable">$&#123;NOWTIME&#125;</span>@<span class="variable">$&#123;MARK&#125;</span>&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; <span class="variable">$&#123;ALTER_LOG&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># awk获取同一收件人、同一告警状态、并且时间是十分钟内的条数</span></span><br><span class="line">        COUNTER_NUMBER=`awk -F<span class="string">&#x27;@&#x27;</span> -v AGOTIME=<span class="variable">$&#123;AGOTIME&#125;</span> <span class="string">&#x27;$1 == &quot;&#x27;</span><span class="variable">$&#123;CONTACT_NAME&#125;</span><span class="string">&#x27;&quot; &amp;&amp; $2&gt;=AGOTIME &amp;&amp; $3 == &quot;&#x27;</span><span class="variable">$&#123;MARK&#125;</span><span class="string">&#x27;&quot;&#x27;</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;ALTER_LOG&#125;</span>|<span class="built_in">wc</span> -l`</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#echo $COUNTER_NUMBER</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 当十分钟告警条数大于等于设置的值时</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> [ <span class="variable">$&#123;COUNTER_NUMBER&#125;</span> -ge <span class="variable">$&#123;WARN_COUNTER&#125;</span> ];<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># 如果.lock文件存在，说明已经发送过一条抑制后的信息了，直接退出，不发送</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> [ -f <span class="variable">$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;</span> ];<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                CHANGE=1</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 发送设置抑制后的告警信息</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> [ <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;MARK&#125;</span>&quot;</span> == <span class="string">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> ];<span class="keyword">then</span></span><br><span class="line">                    message=<span class="string">&quot;## [error]故障:<span class="subst">$(date +&#x27;%F %T&#x27;)</span> 出现大量故障报警,请查看[zabbix页面: <span class="variable">$&#123;zabbix_url&#125;</span>](<span class="variable">$&#123;zabbix_url&#125;</span>)&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">                    message=<span class="string">&quot;## [ok]恢复:<span class="subst">$(date +&#x27;%F %T&#x27;)</span> 出现大量恢复报警,请查看[zabbix页面: <span class="variable">$&#123;zabbix_url&#125;</span>](<span class="variable">$&#123;zabbix_url&#125;</span>)&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># 超过次数则创建lock文件,创建这个文件之前,并没有退出.</span></span><br><span class="line">            [ ! -f <span class="variable">$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;</span> ] &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">touch</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">#echo &#x27;touch lock file&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># 没有操作次数则删除lock文件.</span></span><br><span class="line">            [ -f <span class="variable">$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;</span> ] &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">rm</span> -f <span class="variable">$&#123;LOCK_LAST&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">#echo &#x27;remove lock file&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">fi</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 发送至企业微信机器人</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="title">SEND_MSG</span></span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    wechat_robot_url=<span class="string">&#x27;https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/webhook/send?key=&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    wechat_robot_key=<span class="string">&#x27;robot_token_key&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    url=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;wechat_robot_url&#125;</span><span class="variable">$&#123;wechat_robot_key&#125;</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    msg=<span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$1</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    json_data=<span class="string">&quot;&#123;\&quot;msgtype\&quot;: \&quot;markdown\&quot;,\&quot;markdown\&quot;: &#123;\&quot;content\&quot;: \&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;msg&#125;</span>\&quot;&#125;&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    curl -s -H <span class="string">&quot;Content-Type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span> -d <span class="string">&quot;<span class="variable">$&#123;json_data&#125;</span>&quot;</span> <span class="variable">$&#123;url&#125;</span> &gt; /dev/null</span><br><span class="line"